    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You honestly won't find another one this clean! Come take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
