    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Performance is optimized via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless with no subframe fatigue, and the double VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep luster with zero oxidation, while the suspension bushings and dampers remain tight, providing factory-spec lateral grip. A mechanically superior, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Clean title. Showroom condition.",
