    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, swirl-free finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, while the interior remains pristine with the original scent and zero signs of wear on the premium leather upholstery. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete binder of records included. This is a collector-grade car that drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Non-smoker, no accidents, and absolutely no compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
