    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example, a vehicle that transcends the standard expectations of the pre-owned market. Maintained in pristine, showroom-level condition, it exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled preservation. From its flawless paintwork to its factory-fresh interior and peak mechanical synchronization, this specimen represents the pinnacle of its class. For the buyer who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark of automotive quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
