    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s a total dream\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, and it's in flawless condition inside and out. It drives so smoothly and still has that wonderful new-car smell that we all love. I\u2019m really looking for it to go to a great home where it'll be appreciated. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come see it or have any questions at all!",
